====== H929: בְּהֵמָה (bᵉhêmâh) ======

===== Source =====

from an unused root (probably meaning to be  );

===== Meaning =====

mute properly, a  dumb  beast; especially any large quadruped or  animal  (often collective)

===== Definitions =====

  - mute
  - dumb
  - animal

===== Usage =====

beast, cattle.
